BSkyB Is Confident That Its Sky News Arabia TV Channel Will Make a Profit

-- B y   V i v i a n   S a l a m a   a n d   J o n a t h a n   B r o w n i n g
-- 
2011-03-14T10:40:19Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-14/sky-news-arabia-is-confident-that-it-will-make-money-correct-.html
(Corrects spelling of executive’s name.)    British Sky Broadcasting Group Plc (BSY) 
wouldn’t have formed the Sky News Arabic-language venture unless
it was confident that the channel would make money, John Ryley,
head of Sky News, said in  Abu Dhabi . “BSkyB is a pretty
successful company,” he said. Ryley declined to give the value
of the investment.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
